.B \-\-auditPath
New in version 2.6.

.sp
Specifies the output file for \fBauditing\fP if
\fI\-\-auditDestination\fP has value of \fBfile\fP\&. The \fI\-\-auditPath\fP
option can take either a full path name or a relative path name.
